  "Description": {
    "English": "Emergency <span class=\"name name-fuel\">life support fuel</span>.<br><br>Synthesized from <span class=\"name name-technology\">rocket fuel crystals</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">carbon</span>, this gel offers a temporary boost to life support systems. Long-term impact on user's lungs is currently unknown.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "紧急<span class=\"name name-fuel\">维生凝胶</span>。<br><br>这种凝胶从<span class=\"name name-technology\">火箭燃料水晶</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>中合成，可以为维生系统提供暂时的加持。目前还不知道对使用者肺部的长期影响。",
    "TencentChinese": "紧急<span class=\"name name-fuel\">维生凝胶</span>。<br><br>这种凝胶从<span class=\"name name-technology\">火箭燃料水晶</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>中合成，可以为维生系统提供暂时的加持。目前还不知道对使用者肺部的长期影响。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "緊急<span class=\"name name-fuel\">維生系統燃料</span>。<br><br>這種膠狀物質由<span class=\"name name-technology\">火箭燃料晶體</span>與<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>合成而來，能暫時強化維生系統。對使用者肺部的長期影響目前還不明朗。"
  },
