  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Life Support Gel from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Di-hydrogen Jelly</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Carbon</span>. Use <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> to craft in empty <span class=\"name name-technology\">Inventory Slots</span>.<br>Refine or craft <span class=\"name name-technology\">Di-hydrogen Jelly</span> from the blue <span class=\"name name-technology\">Di-hydrogen Crystals</span> found on all worlds. Use the Scanner (<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>) to locate crystals.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢凝胶</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>制作维生凝胶。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">栏位</span>中制作。<br>使用在所有星球上都能找到的蓝色<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢晶体</span>精炼或制作<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢凝胶</span>。使用扫描仪（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）来定位晶体。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢凝胶</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>制作维生凝胶。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">栏位</span>中制作。<br>使用在所有星球上都能找到的蓝色<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢晶体</span>精炼或制作<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢凝胶</span>。使用扫描仪（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）来定位晶体。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氫膠</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>製作維生膠。使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> 在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">道具欄欄位</span>中製作。<br>使用在所有星球上都能找到的藍色<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氫結晶</span>精製或製作<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氫膠</span>。使用掃描器 (<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>) 來定位晶體。"
